official_title: A bill to provide for the disposal of certain Federal property on the Newlands Project, Nev.

summary.text: Authorizes the Secretary of the Interior to sell specified Federal properties on the Newlands project, Nevada. Provides that sales shall be by public auction to the highest qualified bidder. States that proceeds from the sale of the property shall be available for expenditure by the Secretary for the construction of operation headquarters of the Newlands project.
